'''Gorgal Springs''', based in [[Bestine (city)/Legends|Bestine]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]], was the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] largest producer of pure, natural spring [[Water/Legends|water]]. Crates from the springs were used by [[Gilramos Libkath]] to [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggle]] the weapons he stole from [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba Desilijic Tiure]].

